Author:  MAY
Vol / Page:  527
Edition:  1962
Quote:  FOSSICKER: `the fossicker is to the miner as the gleaner is to the reaper'. The fossicker picks out crevices or pockets but does not work the ground systematically. Often he did not hold a miner's right.
